definition: to change/to become different/to transform/to vary/rebellion
to change into/to turn into/to become
deformation/to become deformed/to change shape/to morph

sentences.english: We expect yield curves to steepen significantly over the medium term.
sentences.chinese: 我們預計收益率曲線將在中期顯著變陡。

sentences.english: Stars become the official page, the stars become the novel to read.
sentences.chinese: 星辰變官方頁面，星辰變小說閱讀。

sentences.english: Stars become the official page, the stars become the novel to read.

sentences.english: The finite element analysis (FEA) and the variable density methods were used. The optimization method and process were presented.
sentences.chinese: 採用有限元法與變密度法，給出了優化方法和步驟。

sentences.english: All things change, and we change with them.
sentences.chinese: 萬物皆變，吾人亦當以變應之。

sentences.english: The origin type of ore deposit is a subvolcanic hydrothermal gold - bearing , altered rock type.
sentences.chinese: 礦牀成因類型爲次火山熱液含金蝕變巖型。

sentences.english: Schwannomas and neurofibromas are benign lesions that are thought to arise from neoplastic transformation of nerve sheath cells.
sentences.chinese: 前兩者是良性腫瘤，一般認爲來自神經鞘細胞的瘤變。

sentences.english: They that were sometime my counsellors, have abhorred me: and he whom I love most is turned against me.
sentences.chinese: 我的知交密友都憎惡我，我所愛的人也對我變了臉。

sentences.english: I'm not sure that they keep me young.
sentences.chinese: 我不能確定這遊戲是否曾讓我變年輕。

sentences.english: The tools she solidifies helps change an industry for the better.
sentences.chinese: 她開發的東西是能讓這個行業變的更好的東西。

sentences.english: Life changes, circumstances change and with that your goals will naturally change as well.
sentences.chinese: 生活變了，環境變了，你的目標自然也會變。

sentences.english: Varying working condition of deep-well water source heat pump are obtained by experiment simulation.
sentences.chinese: 通過實驗模擬了深井水源熱泵制熱變工況運行。

sentences.english: Since then, the styles have changed, different types of watches have been added to the repartee .
sentences.chinese: 從那時起，風格變了，不同類型的手錶被添加到妙答。

sentences.english: The schoolgirl developed long legs, her jawline changed, she had her hair cut.
sentences.chinese: 她雙腿變得修長，下巴輪廓變了，頭髮也剪短了。

sentences.english: The Longyan kaolin deposit in Fujian province, is of weathering residual type of altered granite.
sentences.chinese: 福建龍巖高嶺土礦牀是蝕變花崗岩風化殘餘型礦牀。

sentences.english: Has your practice amount changed throughout your dancing career?
sentences.chinese: 在你的舞蹈生涯裏，你練舞的時間表會經常變嗎？
